  "strategies": [
    {
      "id": "strat-money",
      "title": "💰 賺錢小技巧",
      "class": "class=\"bg-white border shadow-sm p-8 relative\"",
      "html": "<h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-6 flex items-center\">💰 賺錢小技巧</h3>\n                    <div class=\"space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">\n                        <div>\n                            <p class=\"font-bold text-blue-800 mb-1\">1. 解冰果</p>\n                            <p>按C開啟選單➡️ 左方點選最新資訊➡️ 打開冰果任務（或/ob open ）</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                            <p class=\"font-bold text-blue-800 mb-1\">2. 投票赚金幣</p>\n                            <p>在主城輸入/vote 到網站後輸入ID驗證就可以拿投票積分 1點積分可以兌換300 或是兌換其他好物（百變怪）每日都可以投1票</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                            <p class=\"font-bold text-blue-800 mb-1\">3.線上獎勵赚金幣</p>\n                            <p>輸入/pm 可以觀看線上獎勵 點擊領取到郵箱領出來就可以了</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                            <p class=\"font-bold text-blue-800 mb-1\">4.全球市場（GTS)</p>\n                            <p>可以把自己的寶可夢或物品出售上去<br>（有毅力可以找個村莊刷個修補村民）</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                            <p class=\"font-bold text-blue-800 mb-1\">5.幫工</p>\n                            <p>伺服器有時會有玩家招工人（可能幫忙蓋房子挖石頭）</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                            <p class=\"font-bold text-blue-800 mb-1\">6.商店收購</p>\n                            <p>有些玩家商店會收購材料或方塊，可以蒐集需要的物品至玩家商店販售</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                            <p class=\"font-bold text-blue-800 mb-1\">7.設置箱子商店</p>\n                            <p>可以透過「<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"navigateToResult('strategy', 'strat-chestshop', false)\" class=\"text-blue-500 underline hover:text-blue-700 font-bold\">箱子商店</a>」建立自己的自動化店面。</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>"
    },
    {
      "id": "strat-chestshop",
      "title": "📦 如何設置箱子商店？",
      "class": "class=\"bg-white border shadow-sm p-8 relative\"",
      "html": "<h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-6 flex items-center\">📦 如何設置箱子商店？</h3>\n                    <div class=\"space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">\n                        <p>放置一個箱子或木桶</p>\n                        <p>右手拿著想要販售的物品，對著箱子按左鍵，聊天欄會跑出提示，依照提示直接輸入價格數字就設置完成了。</p>\n                        <p class=\"bg-red-50 p-4 border-l-4 border-red-500 text-red-700 font-bold\">⚠️ 如果還沒設置完跑開會自動取消設置</p>\n                    </div>"
    },
    {
      "id": "strat-breeding",
      "title": "🥚 孵蛋教學",
      "class": "class=\"bg-white border shadow-sm p-8 relative\"",
      "html": "<h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-6 flex items-center\">🥚 孵蛋教學</h3>\n                    <div class=\"mb-8\">\n                        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-blue-800 border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-3 mb-4\">繁殖基本條件</h4>\n                        <div class=\"space-y-3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">\n                            <p>進行寶可夢繁殖前，請先確認以下條件：</p>\n                            <ul class=\"list-disc ml-6 space-y-2\">\n                                <li>必須有一隻公寶可夢＋一隻母寶可夢</li>\n                                <li>兩隻寶可夢需屬於 相同蛋群（蛋種）</li>\n                                <li>蛋群查詢網站：<a href=\"https://wiki.52poke.com/wiki/%E6%80%AA%E5%85%BD%EF%BC%88%E8%9B%8B%E7%BE%A4%EF%BC%89\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"text-blue-500 underline hover:text-blue-700\">神奇寶貝百科</a></li>\n                                <li>將兩隻寶可夢放入 牧場（點開牧場介面將一公一母放進去即可開始生蛋）</li>\n                                <li class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">⚠️ 要記得牧場介面右上角孵蛋開關要打開（預設為關閉）</li>\n                            </ul>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"mb-8\">\n                        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-blue-800 border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-3 mb-4\">繁殖知識說明</h4>\n                        <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                            <div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded border\">\n                                <p class=\"font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1\">蛋生成時間</p>\n                                <p class=\"text-gray-600\">• 每 10 分鐘有 <strong>50% 機率</strong> 生成 1 顆蛋</p>\n                                <p class=\"text-gray-600\">• 有機率生出壞蛋，所以有些蛋孵出來數值會莫名很低。</p>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                                <div class=\"border p-4\">\n                                    <p class=\"font-bold text-red-600 mb-2\">🔴 紅線</p>\n                                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">子代 6 項個體值中，會隨機繼承父母的 <strong>5 項</strong>。</p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"border p-4\">\n                                    <p class=\"font-bold text-gray-600 mb-2\">⚪ 不變之石</p>\n                                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">子代 <strong>性格 100% 繼承</strong> 該攜帶者的性格。</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-blue-800 border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-3 mb-4\">六大「鎖V」道具（個體值繼承）</h4>\n                        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3\">\n                            <div class=\"p-3 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 rounded text-center\"><p class=\"font-bold text-blue-900\">力量負重</p><p class=\"text-xs\">遺傳 HP</p></div>\n                            <div class=\"p-3 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 rounded text-center\"><p class=\"font-bold text-blue-900\">力量護腕</p><p class=\"text-xs\">遺傳 攻擊</p></div>\n                            <div class=\"p-3 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 rounded text-center\"><p class=\"font-bold text-blue-900\">力量腰帶</p><p class=\"text-xs\">遺傳 防禦</p></div>\n                            <div class=\"p-3 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 rounded text-center\"><p class=\"font-bold text-blue-900\">力量鏡</p><p class=\"text-xs\">遺傳 特攻</p></div>\n                            <div class=\"p-3 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 rounded text-center\"><p class=\"font-bold text-blue-900\">力量束帶</p><p class=\"text-xs\">遺傳 特防</p></div>\n                            <div class=\"p-3 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 rounded text-center\"><p class=\"font-bold text-blue-900\">力量護踝</p><p class=\"text-xs\">遺傳 速度</p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>"
    },
    {
      "id": "strat-stats",
      "title": "📊 個體值 (IVs) 與努力值 (EVs)",
      "class": "class=\"bg-white border shadow-sm p-8 relative\"",
      "html": "<h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-6 flex items-center\">📊 個體值 (IVs) 與努力值 (EVs)</h3>\n                    <div class=\"mb-8\">\n                        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-blue-800 border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-3 mb-4\">個體值 (IVs) - 天生潛力</h4>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">每項數值最高為 31，也就是俗稱的 <strong>\"V\"</strong>。6項全部31即為 6V。</p>\n                        <div class=\"bg-blue-50 p-4 border rounded\">\n                            <p class=\"font-bold mb-2\">如何查看？</p>\n                            <p class=\"text-sm\">在隊伍選單中對寶可夢點擊 <kbd contenteditable=\"false\">M</kbd> 查看詳細資訊，切換至「數值」分頁即可看到 0~31 的數字。</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-blue-800 border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-3 mb-4\">努力值 (EVs) - 後天訓練</h4>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-2\">單項上限 252，全項總計上限 510。每 4 點努力值可增加 1 點實質數值。</p>\n                        <div class=\"mt-4 p-4 bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400\">\n                            <p class=\"text-gray-800 font-bold\">💡 小提醒：</p>\n                            <p class=\"text-gray-700 mt-1 text-lg\">按 <kbd class=\"bg-white px-2 border\" contenteditable=\"false\">C</kbd> 選擇 EVS 訓練可至訓練場練<span class=\"text-red-600 bg-yellow-200 px-1 font-black\">等級</span>及<span class=\"text-blue-700 bg-yellow-200 px-1 font-black\">努力值</span>。</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>"
    },
    {
      "id": "strat-nature",
      "title": "🎭 性格加成對照表",
      "class": "class=\"bg-white border shadow-sm p-8 relative\"",
      "html": "<h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-green-900 mb-6 flex items-center\">🎭 性格加成對照表</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">性格會影響兩項數值，一項增加 10% (紅色)，一項減少 10% (藍色)。</p>\n                    <div class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n                        <table class=\"w-full text-center text-sm border-collapse border border-gray-200\">\n                            <thead><tr class=\"bg-green-100 font-bold\">\n                                <th class=\"border p-2\">性格</th><th class=\"border p-2\">增加 (1.1x)</th><th class=\"border p-2\">減少 (0.9x)</th><th class=\"border p-2\">推薦用途</th>\n                            </tr></thead>\n                            <tbody>\n                                <tr><td class=\"border p-2 font-bold\">固執 (Adamant)</td><td class=\"border p-2 text-red-600\">攻擊</td><td class=\"border p-2 text-blue-600\">特攻</td><td class=\"border p-2\">物攻手</td></tr>\n                                <tr><td class=\"border p-2 font-bold\">內斂 (Modest)</td><td class=\"border p-2 text-red-600\">特攻</td><td class=\"border p-2 text-blue-600\">攻擊</td><td class=\"border p-2\">特攻手</td></tr>\n                                <tr><td class=\"border p-2 font-bold\">爽朗 (Jolly)</td><td class=\"border p-2 text-red-600\">速度</td><td class=\"border p-2 text-blue-600\">特攻</td><td class=\"border p-2\">高速物攻手</td></tr>\n                                <tr><td class=\"border p-2 font-bold\">膽小 (Timid)</td><td class=\"border p-2 text-red-600\">速度</td><td class=\"border p-2 text-blue-600\">攻擊</td><td class=\"border p-2\">高速特攻手</td></tr>\n                                <tr><td class=\"border p-2 font-bold\">大膽 (Bold)</td><td class=\"border p-2 text-red-600\">防禦</td><td class=\"border p-2 text-blue-600\">攻擊</td><td class=\"border p-2\">物理肉盾</td></tr>\n                            </tbody>\n                        </table>\n                    </div>"
    }
  ]
}